Answers or Assumptions:

    1.How is search functionality designed?
    It’s plain key word search

    2.Will there be any auto suggest based on recent user search history?
    This will be our future enhancement

    3.Can we search book by?
            Author – Yes
            Title	- Yes
            Key word (ex. Action, Drama, Comic, Fiction) - Yes

   4. How are Search results displayed?
    Search results displayed based on keyword ‘contains’

    5.How is the book share designed?
    Currently link will be shared when user clicks on the link, users should be forced to install app to read it
    Users base can grow for app!

    6.Can we save the book for future reading?
    Future enhancement after login or user registration functionality is implemented

    7.Can we rate the book?
    May be in future enhancement